---
title: Beef and Zucchini Yakitori-Style Bowl with Zucchini and Sesame Rice
description: This delicious Japanese number is bound to be a crowd-pleaser! We've removed the skewers from this yakitori dish to make it family friendly and added some green onion rice and hearty zucchini.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-and-zucchini-yakitori-style-bowl-67587ebf.jpg
